Celebrating his 50th birthday and eight years after his death, Provogue Records releases Heal My Soul - the first album of new songs recorded by Jeff Healey in more than 15 years. It has been lovingly put together under the direct supervision of the Jeff Healey Estate. Healey died on March 2, 2008, after a three-year battle with cancer, during which he continued to gig and record.
